snippet.title: 24LED EMERGENCY BEACON WARNING HAZARD FLASH CAR TRUCK AMBER/WHITE STROBE LIGHT
snippet.description:
Product Features:

UPGRADE: Diecast Aluminum Housing & Ultra-thin design.24 LED as light source, offers a super bright light output, can be seen on a bright clear day.

HIGH PERFORMANCE: Integrated heatsink, and anti-condensation drain port, Waterproof and dust-proof, and corrosion-resistant.

18 STROBE PATTERNS: Built-in flasher, 18 select-able flashing patterns; Last pattern recall/memory function.

UNIVERSAL 12V-24V: Fits for any public utility vehicles, construction vehicles, tow trucks, snowplows, emergency medical vehicles, ambulances, oversize load vehicles, slow vehicles

EASY TO INSTALL: 3 wires connection; Free Screws &Protection Pad to Attach to The Grille or Bumper.

Product Specification:

Type: Strobe Flashing Light Bars

LED Model: 3030

Number of Chips: 24pcs/Bulbs

Number of Bulbs: 2

Color: Amber/White

Patterns: 18 different flashing patterns

Voltage: 12-24V

Power: 72W (3W/LED)

Waterproof Level: IPX-4

Lifespan: 50,000 hours

Material: Diecast Aluminum Housing + PC Lens

Size: L 7.48" (190mm) W 1.1" (27mm) H 0.4"(11mm)

Weight: 152g

Placement on Vehicle: Front, Rear, Left, Right

Application: Signal light, Daytime running light, Fog light, etc.

Application-2: For Construction / Towing / Slow-moving Truck.

Application-3: Vehicle Auto Car Pick Up Truck SUV ATV UTV Trailer

Fitment Type: Direct Replacement

Package Included

2pcs 24 LED Emergency Flashing Light Bars Amber White

2x Protection Pad

4x Screws
